data/resources/4121/11.02.503.pdf"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.ilpa.org.uk/data/resources/4121/11.02.503.pdf</span></a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:11pt"> </span><br /><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_GoBack"></a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><div style="width:auto; height:auto; float:left;"><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">25</span></p></div><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div><hr style="width:33%; height:1px; text-align:left" /><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn1"></a><a href="#_ftnref1">[1]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">HL Report, </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">21 Nov 2011: Column 821.</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">See</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> also HL Report </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt">5 Mar 2012 : Column 1570.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn2"></a><a href="#_ftnref2">[2]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> Form CIV ECF 1.See </span><a href="http://www.justice.gov.uk/legal-aid/funding/exceptional-cases-funding"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.justice.gov.uk/legal-aid/funding/exceptional-cases-funding</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn3"></a><a href="#_ftnref3">[3]</a><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:10pt"> Available at </span><a href="http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/forms/legal-aid/civil-forms/ecf1.pdf"><span style=